Gomora actress and Boom Shaka singer Thembi Seete finally revealed the face of her child to the public during his birthday celebration. Thembi is very private about her love life and that of her son, who turned four. The actress only ever shared that she was pregnant, but never revealed who the father of her child is, or who she is romantically involved with. But on Monday and Tuesday the proud mommy shared pictures from the birthday party on her public social media platforms, wishing her son a happy birthday, and shared how he had been a blessing to her and his father.   For the latest entertainment news from Sunday World, click here. Or read the latest from Shwashwi here. Follow @SundayWorldZA on Twitter and @sundayworldza on Instagram, or like our Facebook Page, Sunday World, by clicking here for the latest breaking news in South Africa. To Subscribe to Sunday World, click here.